mv                                    macro                                   mv

NAME
     mmvv and uummvv - move one motor

SYNOPSIS

     mmvv mmoottoorr uusseerr__vvaalluuee
     uummvv mmoottoorr uusseerr__vvaalluuee

DESCRIPTION

     The mmvv macro moves mmoottoorr to the user angle given by uusseerr__vvaalluuee.

     The uummvv macro also moves the motor, but provides an updated display of the
     motor position on the screen while the motor is moving.  The update
     interval, in seconds, is set by the global variable UUPPDDAATTEE.

EXAMPLE

     mmvv tthh 00

SEE ALSO

     _m_v_d _m_v_r _m_o_t_o_r_s _w_a_i_t

